  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Binder
    The Binder class serves as the abstract base class for different types of card binders.
    CollectorBinder
    The CollectorBinder class represents a specialized binder that only accepts cards with either Rarity.RARE or Rarity.LEGENDARY rarity and a variant other than Variant.NORMAL.
    LuxuryBinder
    The LuxuryBinder class represents a special type of SellableBinder that only accepts cards with variants other than NORMAL.
    NonCuratedBinder
    The NonCuratedBinder class represents a basic type of Binder with no restrictions on the types of cards that can be added.
    PauperBinder
    The PauperBinder class is a specialized SellableBinder that only accepts cards with Rarity.COMMON or Rarity.UNCOMMON rarity.
    RaresBinder
    Represents a binder that only accepts rare and legendary cards.
    SellableBinder
    An abstract class representing a binder that can be sold.
